egenden Werk ein Beitrag zur Bewertung der Sicherheit und Vorteilhaftigkeit von gedeckten Schuldverschreibungen und zur Diskussion der Integration der EU-Hypothekarkreditmärkte und insbesondere zur Refinanzierung des Hypothekarkredits mittels gedeckter Schuldverschreibungen geleistet werden."  aThis handbook on the new bond law provides a legal comparison to the UK covered bond. While offering a deeper understanding of structured covered bonds and the further development of national law, the work at hand also aims to contribute to the assessment of the security and benefits of covered bonds and the discussion of integration of the EU mortgagee credit markets, especially regarding the refinancing of mortgage credits through covered bonds.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAsset-backed financingxLaw and legislationzGermany. 0aAsset-backed financingxLaw and legislationzGreat Britain. 0aBond marketzGermany. 0aBonds marketzGreat Britain. 0aBondsxLaw and legislationzGermany. 0aBondsxLaw and legislationzGreat Britain. 0aMortgage-backed securitiesxLaw and legislationzGermany. 0aMortgage-backed securitiesxLaw and legislationzGreat Britain. 4aPfandbrief. 4aSchuldverschreibung. 7aLAW / Commercial / General.2bisacsh  aBonds.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2009z9783110219517oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2009z9783899496871oZDB-23-DGC0 cprintz978389949649940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978389949650540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783899496505423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783899496505/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA